    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>保羅事奉神的目的為何？</strong></p><p>他的目的是要建立神選民的信心，及建立真理的知識。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56001001",
