      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 473485,
    "reference_id": 133849,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "提多書 1:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>監督應具備哪些好的品性？</strong></p><p>監督應該樂意接待，喜愛良善，明智，公正，聖潔，和自制。 </p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "56001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "TIT 1:8",
          "end_ref": "56001008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "TIT 1:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 473486,
    "reference_id": 133850,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "提多書 1:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>監督對所學的道理應抱持什麼態度？</strong></p><p>他必須堅守所學，從而能夠鼓勵人和駁倒他人。</p>",
