    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 473490,
    "reference_id": 133854,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "提多書 1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>保羅說，他們不應該聽從什麼？</strong></p><p>他們不應該聽從猶太人荒渺的言語和人的誡命。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
