    "reference_id": 133856,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "提多書 1:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56001016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>雖然污穢的人自稱認識神，但他如何拒絕祂？</strong></p><p>他在行事上拒絕神。</p>",
