  {
    "content_id": 473498,
    "reference_id": 133862,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "提多書 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "56002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><strong>身為奴隸的信徒們要如何行事為人？</strong></p><p>他們要順服他們的主人，討人喜歡，不應該頂嘴。</p>",
